Package edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_tracker.model.log

Class AbstractTaskLog

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_tracker.model.log.AbstractTaskLog
Direct Known Subclasses:
AllTasksLog, CategoryLog
public abstract class AbstractTaskLog extends Object
The AbstractTaskLog class is an abstract class at the top of the hierarchy for lists of logged tasks. The AbstractTaskLog knows its takLogName and the ILogList of Tasks.
Author:
Diya Patel, Jayani Sivakumar
